   "source": [
    "# Numpy的梯度函数\n",
    "\n",
    "- gradient(a) 计算数组a中元素的梯度，当a为多维数组时，返回每个维度的梯度\n",
    "\n",
    "梯度：连续值之前的变化率，即斜率\n",
    "\n",
    "如果xy坐标轴连续三个x坐标对应的y轴值为a,b,c，则b的梯度为：(c-a) / 2"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "array([14,  8,  9,  6, 13])"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 3,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "a = np.random.randint(0, 20, (5,))\n",
    "a"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "array([-6. , -2.5, -1. ,  2. ,  7. ])"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 4,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "np.gradient(a)"
   ]
